Question 2:

/usr/sbin/sendmail -> lien vers /etc/alternatives/mta
/etc/init.d/sendmail -> script d'arret et de demarrage
/etc/rc3.d/S80Sendmail -> lien vers /etc/init.d/sendmail
/etc/rc5.d/S80Sendmail -> lien vers /etc/init.d/sendmail

Question 3:
Il a fallu installer xinetd : yum install xinetd
/etc/init.d/xinetd start -> demarre le daemon
/etc/init.d/xinetd stop  -> arrete le daemon

